title: COVID-19: Spread situation by prefecture in Japan
description: COVID-19: Spread situation by prefecture in JapanI will zoom into Japan in this kernel, to visualize how Coronavirus spread in each prefecture in Japan. The 2 external dataset is used:  Japan COVID-19 by prefecture: Individual covid confirmed case's precise information in Japan. Data is from kaz-ogiwara/covid19  Japan Prefecture Latitude Longitude: It stores longitude, latitude information of each prefecture in Japan. Japan population by age and sex in 2020: Precise population information in Japan.  Please upvote both kernel & dataset if you find it useful :)
